{"tid":2078884,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【喵家姐】不理奶奶反對收養病貓 新手媽媽拒棄養：兩個都係仔女要養一世","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T04:33:37.000Z","uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d627d8ea986e2f9de34246dfccf7c47f99f62f","tid":2078884,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6DDaKzYqTD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6DDaKzYqTD4&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1e3f647f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6DDaKzYqTD4</a><br />\n<br />\n準媽媽因種種緣故棄養貓咪之事時有聽聞，如藝人應采兒怕貓毛引起BB皮膚敏感或哮喘，陳茵媺則因為要停服敏感藥而忍痛別貓。但對新手媽媽Kiki來說，所有理由她都不會認同。就在兒子出生前兩個月，她不理家人反對，決定收養一隻被遺棄的病貓。<br />\n<br />\n========= <br />\n全新副刊，推動知識文化多元。培養品味，立足香港放眼世界。不畏高牆，我們站在雞蛋一方。<br />\n《果籽》 栽種品味，一籽了然。<br />\n<a href=\"http://as.appledaily.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fas.appledaily.com%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=9fb62c56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fas.appledaily.com%2F&h=badf2ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://as.appledaily.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsAZBiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsAZBiK.jpg&h=6f821c87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5472929795eb6a7980af5e00c8533c1b4f99f2f","tid":2078884,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"53c8a12b1c9d707137cd09b177aca31b4daaba4b","tid":2078884,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"